  "title": "Client Advisor (Basic + Allowance + Commission)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leading insurer in Singapore. They have a few openings for the Client Advisor position<br /></p><p><strong>You will be based in one of the outlets island-wide in Singapore !</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to walk-in customers and recommending the most appropriate products to the customers</li><li>Speak to the customers, provide good financial advice and tailored financial solutions based on customers' requirements</li><li>Built good relationship with new and existing customers</li><li>Contribute to the sales team, helping your teammates to succeed and achieve their sales targets</li><li>Attend events, roadshows to get more sales opportunities</li><li>Cold calling, set appointments and meet more customers </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in related discipline</li><li>No experience is required, training will be provided</li><li>A passion for sales, love interacting with customers</li><li>Able to work as a team, helping each other to succeed</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Applicants who are interested in insurance sales are most welcome to apply!<br /></p><p>Applicants who are interested to apply for this position can send your latest resume to alfred.lai@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg<br /></p><p>Alfred Lai<br />EA Reg No: R1545971<br />EA License No: 21C0434</p><p><br /></p>",
